texts.text: Xbox 360 Edition 1.66.0016.0
Build 0016 was a developer version of Xbox 360 Edition showcased at MineCon 2011.[1][2] This version is based off of Java Edition Beta 1.6.6.
Contents

1 Features
2 Trivia
3 Gallery
4 References
5 External links
Features

All features from and before Java Edition Beta 1.6.6.
Console-exclusive controls and menus.
Includes a tutorial world.
Trivia
This is the first ever version of Minecraft to release on the Xbox 360.
